            <h3 class="horizontal-line bg-fuelit">Postgres</h3>
            <p>Being ACID-compliant Postgres provides full support for foreign keys, views, joins, stored procedures, and triggers, in various languages. Along with that, Postgres also houses some robust set of features like multi-version concurrency (MVCC), point-in-time recovery, granular access controls, and many more.</p>
