            <h3 class="horizontal-line bg-fuelit">AWS</h3>
            <p>Amazon Web Services is a subsidiary of Amazon providing on-demand cloud computing platforms and APIs on a metered pay-as-you-go basis. It provides a fast, flexible, secure, and budget-friendly solution for businesses.</p>
